ruyan su casa una vez que se casen." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3047000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentRatingKey="67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Trepadora" grandparentType="show" index="17" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" title="S01:E017" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E017" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E017" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E017" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1773578396" duration="3046000" endsAt="1773581442" id="69ad6c81182d3d80391ee1eb" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1773609355" duration="2913000" endsAt="1773612268" id="69ad6c81182d3d80391ee1f5" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video guid="plex://episode/69ac1b062d5af6ce92de66d1" key="/library/metadata/69ac1b062d5af6ce92de66d1" ratingKey="69ac1b062d5af6ce92de66d1" summary="Torrealba expone ante dos oficiales el caso del crimen de Ezequiel López Méndez, es interrumpido por Marcelina que viene a confesarse culpable, Torrealba no le cree. Rosa acusa a Octavia de ser la que ideó abandonar a Camila y convenció a Marcelina de que lo hiciere. Octavia se burla y Camila, ciega de ira la bota de su casa." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3020000" grand